messages = Array[String](["Well, after weeks without luck, I guess I should go meet this mysterious someone.", "After all the murders my boss gave me this gun for protection, ", "he warned me not to carry it around though… ", "should I take the gun with me?", "", "What good is a gun stashed at home anyway?", "Going unarmed to the middle of nowhere to meet god knows whom? No, thanks.", "I guess I could get in trouble carrying this around, I should leave it at home.", "I don’t have a register for this, plus, I barely know how to use it.", "", "There's no one nearby.", "I guess he or she is going to be late...", "You wait 30 minutes...", "...", "......", "You look at your clock; it's past 11 PM.

", "Okay, I’m beginning to think this was just a prank.", "You wait until midnight...", "...", ".........", "You hear some noises in the woods…", "It's just raccoons rummaging about...", "nothing out of the ordinary.", "It's already close to 1AM...", "I’m getting tired of waiting, this was a waste of time.", "I should head home.", "-", "Sure it beats being touched by that creepy mayor.", "I’m sorry, did you say something?", "It's nothing.", "You close your eyes again.", "There must be a clue here somewhere, something I’m missing.", "As you begin to drift away, there’s a loud noise and the car swirls violently to the left.", "Fortunately, at this hour there wasn’t any incoming traffic.", "WHAT was that?", "Relax, it’s just a flat tire.", "Alright, if you say so…", "The cab driver goes outside to fix it… "])

